# Shopware C# API Connector

  A shopware C# API connector as part of my project to interface the ERP "Sage Line 100" to Shopware
  Used the "shopdoktor" code as a base to start with (see original readme text below)
  
  Actual release is still beta.
  From original repo:
     * numerous fixes (to reflect changed API models in 5.2.x);
	 * added features:
	     * return id of created item (data returned from POST)
		 * ManufacturerResource (as from shopware 5.1.3)
		 * media resource
	     * the ability to add filter and/or sorting (when calling getAll)
	     * first support for translation resource


# Original text from "shopdoktor"

Bitte beachten Sie, dass sich die Software noch in Entwicklung befindet. Für weitere Details können Sie gerne eine Mail an info@shopdoktor.com schreiben.

DEUTSCH:
Weitere Informationen unter: https://www.shopdoktor.com/shopware/plugins/csharp-schnittstelle/

ENGLISH:
See https://www.shopdoktor.com/shopware/plugins/csharp-schnittstelle/ for more details.
